public class HomeActivity
extends com.actionbarsherlock.app.SherlockActivity

This class inherits SherlockActivity and brings the user to the home screen. This is the entry point of the application after logging in. All other base activities are reachable from here, and any additional functionality will most likely be reachable from this activity.
